author: bestplayerever

rate: and I can't stop. Highly recommended.

rate: but it could use some improvements in graphics and controls.

author: eliteplayer

author: gamemaster

author: topgamer

rate: but it has some bugs and glitches that need to be fixed in future updates.

author: nightwarrior

author: frostking

author: starfighter

content: This game was a bit overhyped. The storyline falls flat after a few hours of gameplay.

author: dragonrider

author: swordmaster

rate: this game is for you. The difficulty scales nicely.
